  "instructions": [
    "Preheat grill to medium-high heat.",
    "In a large bowl, whisk together pineapple juice, coconut milk, soy sauce, brown sugar, and fish sauce (if using).",
    "Cut tofu into 1-inch cubes and add to marinade. Let it sit for at least 30 minutes.",
    "Thread tofu, pineapple chunks, and onions onto bamboo skewers, leaving a little space between each piece.",
